summary: Standardizes the names of the \"Mysteries of Talara\" books
descriptionHtml:
Before:
Mystery of Talara, v 1
Mystery of Talara, v 2
Mystery of Talara, v3
Mystery of Talara, Part 4
Mystery of Talara, v5


After:
Mystery of Talara 1
Mystery of Talara 2
Mystery of Talara 3
Mystery of Talara 4
Mystery of Talara 5

Note: some of the Talara books are skill books, so this mod will conflict with any mod that also renames skill books (e.g. Improved Skill Books).
author: dbbolton
